<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='784000' id='t-784000'>those Greeks had some powerful insights.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='787000' id='t-787000'>They knew that a fundamental piece falls into place</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='790000' id='t-790000'>when you start to live out their little phrase,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='793000' id='t-793000'>when you come into contact with yourself.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796000' id='t-796000'>They understood the power of human narrative</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799000' id='t-799000'>and the value that we place on humans</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='801000' id='t-801000'>as changing, evolving and growing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='804000' id='t-804000'>But they understood something more fundamental --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807000' id='t-807000'>the sheer joy in discovery,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810000' id='t-810000'>the delight and fascination that we get from the world</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813000' id='t-813000'>and being ourselves in it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='815000' id='t-815000'>the richness that we get</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='817000' id='t-817000'>from seeing, feeling and knowing the lives that we are.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='820000' id='t-820000'>My mom's an artist,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='822000' id='t-822000'>and as a child I'd often see her bring things to life with the stroke of a brush.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='825000' id='t-825000'>One moment it was all white space, pure possibility.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='828000' id='t-828000'>The next, it was alive</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830000' id='t-830000'>with her colorful ideas and expressions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='833000' id='t-833000'>As I sat easel-side,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='835000' id='t-835000'>watching her transform canvas after canvas,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='838000' id='t-838000'>I learned that you could create your own world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='842000' id='t-842000'>I learned that our own inner worlds --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='844000' id='t-844000'>our ideas, emotions and imaginations --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='847000' id='t-847000'>were, in fact, not bound by our brains and bodies.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='851000' id='t-851000'>If you could think it, if you could discover it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='854000' id='t-854000'>you could bring it to life.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='857000' id='t-857000'>To me, thought-controlled computing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='859000' id='t-859000'>is as simple and powerful as a paintbrush --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861000' id='t-861000'>one more tool to unlock and enliven</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='864000' id='t-864000'>the hidden worlds within us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='866000' id='t-866000'>I look forward to the day</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='868000' id='t-868000'>that I can sit beside you, easel-side,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='871000' id='t-871000'>watching the world that we can create</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='873000' id='t-873000'>with our new toolboxes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='875000' id='t-875000'>and the discoveries that we can make</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='877000' id='t-877000'>about ourselves.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:50
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='879000' id='t-879000'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='881000' id='t-881000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
